<L>__{interior spain nightclub late night}
<A>__{a huge crowd dances fervently to the live spanish music. in the middle of the floor, the spanish players are the life of the party. in a corner, monica sits with sidra, drinking and watching the festivities. a large trophy sits on the table.}
