<D>__{can you take that damn thing off the table.}
<C>__{monica}
<D>__{you mean my championship trophy? my bad.}
<A>__{monica sets it down in the seat next to her, puts an arm around it. sidra shakes her head.}
<C>__{sidra}
<D>__{still a cocky bitch.}
<A>__{monica laughs. she downs her drink, motions to the waiter.}
<C>__{monica}
<D>__{uno mas, por favor.}
<A>__{the waiter nods.}
<C>__{monica }
<D>__{last i heard, you were playing in sweden.}
